Stage 1
Collect 3 digit number from user
Get the first and last digit
Compare the two to see if the number is palindrome
Display if it is a Palindrome

Stage 2
Prompt user to input a number between 0 to 1000
Collect the number from user
Store the number in a variable ifPalin
Perform ifPalin / 100 to get first Digit 
Save the first Digit in a variable firstNo
Perform ifPalin % 10 to get last Digit
Save the last Digit in a variable lastDig
If firstNo is equals lastDig, 
Print number is a palindrome 
Else, print it is not a palindrome